::Battera/DarkMouse::

Battera:  she flew over some mountains.  She let out a sonar screetch to 
find out wha the land scape was so she didn't go craching face first into 
the side of a mountain.

============

DarkMouse:: She checked to scanners and saw a fast moving object.
            "Computer, what is that object passing the base?"

COMPUTER:"Predacon form, signal not known."

DarkMouse:: "Oh great, just what I need, another flyer to get pissed off at 
me.  That's all I need."  She kept an eye on the scanner.
"Good. It appears it will pass by us and not stop." SHe sat back and watched 
the scanner.  The bot passed over the ship and didn't stop.
